criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age from 18 to 75;

          -  Diagnosis of psychosis and / or mood disorder according to DSM-IV (American
             Psychiatric Association, 2000).

          -  both sexes;

          -  users who sign the informed consent;

          -  users under protection for which the informed consent is signed by the guardian

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  The non-satisfaction of the inclusion criteria;

          -  The diagnosis of epilepsy or serious eye diseases, due to the risk associated with the
             excessive stimulation of virtual reality
